27
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:19,820
[Legend of Awakening]

28
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,530
[Episode 7]

29
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:27,978
Don't fight! Calm down. Don't fight!

30
00:02:27,978 --> 00:02:32,560
I got it! That brat must have fled to the back of the hillside.

31
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,230
- I'll take you there.
- Hurry up!

32
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:35,600
- After you!
- Come along!

33
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:38,879
Over here! This way, please.

34
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:42,320
Senior Wei, are you sure Lu Ping will come here?

35
00:02:43,029 --> 00:02:45,399
I went to great lengths to get this information.

36
00:02:45,399 --> 00:02:47,640
That brat always trains at the back of the mountain.

37
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,890
Now, my father came to capture him.

38
00:02:50,890 --> 00:02:54,198
The last fight wasn't enough, I want to kill him this time.

39
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:57,500
Senior Wei, someone is really coming from the Wind Taker Institute.

40
00:02:57,500 --> 00:03:02,298
Stay hidden and don't make any sound! Once they are near, we'll make our move.

41
00:03:02,298 --> 00:03:03,740
- Yes.
- Yes.

42
00:03:09,419 --> 00:03:10,920
Are you guys ready?

43
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,700
Who did that?

44
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:43,018
Brat! You didn't succumb to the poison in the tower last time, I'll kill you today!

45
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:57,859
- Tianqi?
- Father, how could it be you?

46
00:03:57,859 --> 00:04:01,959
I... I... I sacrificed myself to save your father.

47
00:04:01,959 --> 00:04:03,550
Thank you.

48
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:07,550
- Am I dead? Am I dead?
- No, you're not! You're still living.

49
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:10,900
- What's wrong?
- Why does it not hurt? I don't feel pain anymore.

50
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:13,320
Hang on, you're...

51
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:17,060
Get up right now.

52
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:19,660
It's retribution for my sins.

53
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:24,219
I originally wanted you two to lead the attack and capture Lu Ping.

54
00:04:24,219 --> 00:04:26,150
Thank goodness, I walked in front of you.

55
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:30,260
- Otherwise, your son would have...
- Thank you so much.

56
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,999
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

57
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:35,199
Wei Young Lord, what did you mean just now?

58
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:38,299
- You used poison inside the tower?
- I didn't!

59
00:04:38,299 --> 00:04:42,059
Cheating in the exam and poisoning the lives of other test takers.

60
00:04:42,059 --> 00:04:43,920
What kind of crime is this?

61
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,680
Tianqi, don't be afraid!

62
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:50,299
My son would never do such a despicable act.

63
00:04:50,299 --> 00:04:55,358
It was so chaotic just now, maybe you heard it wrongly.

64
00:04:55,358 --> 00:04:58,179
- All of us heard it.
- Your son did it.

65
00:04:58,179 --> 00:05:01,278
Yes! You guys heard it wrongly!

66
00:05:01,278 --> 00:05:04,219
- You guys heard it wrongly; everyone heard it wrongly!
- Yes, they heard it wrongly.

67
00:05:04,219 --> 00:05:06,998
We heard it, Master. We swear!

68
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,720
Actually, I heard it, too.

69
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:13,379
You... How could you?

70
00:05:13,379 --> 00:05:15,410
Come over here!

71
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:20,419
Well, I need a bit of hush money.

72
00:05:20,419 --> 00:05:24,030
We, Wind Taker Institute, isn't as wealthy as that Chan State Academy.

73
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:28,119
We don't accept payment on credit. Cash! Cash is accepted.

74
00:05:28,959 --> 00:05:33,960
Guo Youdao, this is blackmail! You're blackmailing me.

75
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:43,959
They are gone! Every single person from the Wei family has left.

76
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:47,119
I told you! My luck is back again.

77
00:05:47,119 --> 00:05:49,820
- Really?
- Of course!

78
00:05:55,800 --> 00:06:00,400
Brother, they left and we're fine now.

79
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:05,739
Can we still go back?

80
00:06:05,739 --> 00:06:08,858
I already said those things, going back is embarrassing.

81
00:06:11,179 --> 00:06:13,879
Let's go! Let's wait for him at Ruyu House.

82
00:06:13,879 --> 00:06:15,700
Whom are we waiting for?

83
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:19,080
After he arrives, you'll know.

84
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,940
Master,

85
00:06:34,739 --> 00:06:37,060
why did you protect Lu Ping so desperately?

86
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:39,530
You even pretended to be a bad person.

87
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:45,039
No wonder Lu Ping always provokes you.

88
00:06:45,039 --> 00:06:49,239
Now, I also feel that your personality

89
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,600
is quite interesting.

90
00:07:07,859 --> 00:07:09,920
Come with me!

91
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,360
[Ruyu House]

92
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,339
From now on,

93
00:07:25,339 --> 00:07:30,700
you have nothing to do with the Wind Taker Institute.

94
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:35,600
Cutting ties with them is the only way to save them from all this mess.

95
00:07:36,939 --> 00:07:39,700
Brother, he really came.

96
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:42,820
Save me!

97
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:47,340
Mo Lin, Su Tang is your disciple and also my disciple.

98
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:50,779
If I die, I'll never let her take you as her master.

99
00:07:51,819 --> 00:07:53,660
Speak now if you have something to say.

100
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:56,290
You guys can either fight now or get this done with.

101
00:07:56,298 --> 00:07:58,739
Old geezer, I'm going to kill you.

102
00:07:59,499 --> 00:08:03,218
Master, is this why you wanted me to come with you?

103
00:08:03,218 --> 00:08:06,498
Old geezer, I won't let you die instantly.

104
00:08:06,498 --> 00:08:11,319
The Piebald Scorpion Venom on this arrow will make you itch for seven weeks straight.

105
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:15,719
Despicable person! Come here if you dare...

106
00:08:16,379 --> 00:08:17,859
to fight with Xifan.

107
00:08:17,859 --> 00:08:19,499
Let go of Xifan if you dare.

108
00:08:19,499 --> 00:08:22,219
I'll never let him go! Lu Ping, come here.

109
00:08:22,219 --> 00:08:25,078
Perfect timing! Make that brat stop right now.

110
00:08:25,078 --> 00:08:26,879
Am I not rat poop?

111
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:30,339
Assumed I farted loudly that day, can you?

112
00:08:30,339 --> 00:08:32,260
Please don't, Master!

113
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:34,560
Although I'm petty,

114
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:38,010
I really want to talk to you, openly and honestly,

115
00:08:38,619 --> 00:08:41,250
so that you can understand me.

116
00:08:44,939 --> 00:08:49,200
Madam Jin, prepare some dishes and wine.

117
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,159
Put it on my tab.

118
00:08:51,979 --> 00:08:53,679
All right.

119
00:08:55,859 --> 00:08:57,599
Shi Dongchun wine?

120
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:03,170
A pot costs 52 silver taels and one sip is worth three silver taels.

121
00:09:03,859 --> 00:09:07,299
After I finish it, it's gone after I pee.

122
00:09:08,659 --> 00:09:13,839
A fine wine deserves a modest master.

123
00:09:13,839 --> 00:09:18,019
If you didn't use some tricks and wrote the letter to attract Qin Qi,

124
00:09:18,019 --> 00:09:20,840
I'm afraid I'm still trapped in Chan State.

125
00:09:27,899 --> 00:09:32,060
Is your head messed up after getting beaten inside the tower?

126
00:09:32,060 --> 00:09:36,060
I advise you to place your bet on someone else quickly.

127
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,660
Someone else?

128
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,430
I invested too much.

129
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:46,939
If I withdraw halfway, I'll lose everything.

130
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:56,579
As long as I'm still on the gambling table, I can recoup my losses.

131
00:10:14,239 --> 00:10:19,500
Now, we're disqualified from the Pneuma Combat Convention.

132
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:24,039
- Where are you going next?
- I'll follow wherever my brother goes.

133
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:27,839
If we can't go to the convention, there is always another way.

134
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:34,158
Why don't you dump your troublesome brother? Worship me as your master.

135
00:10:54,899 --> 00:10:58,620
You're not bad, it's just that you shouldn't be with us.

136
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:02,219
Don't you want to roam the martial arts world and become the number one assassin?

137
00:11:02,219 --> 00:11:04,839
Actually, I think you're quite impressive.

138
00:11:04,839 --> 00:11:08,859
Maybe next time when we meet, you'll already have become the number one assassin.

139
00:11:11,979 --> 00:11:13,760
The next time we meet...

140
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,280
Why do you look unhappy?

141
00:11:19,019 --> 00:11:22,720
I'm not! I just feel that...

142
00:11:25,239 --> 00:11:30,179
I couldn't get a disciple this time, so I'm feeling quite sad.

143
00:11:46,859 --> 00:11:49,699
Don't worry!

144
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:55,480
You still have a chance.

145
00:11:55,480 --> 00:12:04,040
Su Tang, do you know who is the important person I always visit every year at Kaifeng?

146
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,740
- Who is it?
- Who is it?

147
00:12:12,110 --> 00:12:15,520
Chu Min? Shining Sky Academy's instructor?

148
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:19,120
So, the person you go visit every year at Kaifeng is her?

149
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:23,239
I can't believe an old man like you have such an influential friend.

150
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:27,540
So you decided to stop calling me an old geezer?

151
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,940
Listen carefully!

152
00:12:29,739 --> 00:12:32,799
The Pneuma Combat Convention requires a team of four people to compete.

153
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:36,138
The tower was demolished, so Wind Takers have already been disqualified.

154
00:12:36,138 --> 00:12:39,379
But if you guys worship Chu Min as your master,

155
00:12:39,379 --> 00:12:43,900
we can use Shining Sky Academy's name to join the convention.

156
00:12:43,900 --> 00:12:47,538
Surpass Big Dippers and make our ancestors proud; both can be achieved!

157
00:12:47,538 --> 00:12:50,220
Lu Ping already agreed to it.

158
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:53,020
If Brother agrees, I agree, too.

159
00:12:54,080 --> 00:13:00,278
Fine! I'll do this kind deed for my future disciple and let you guys owe me a favor.

160
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:16,579
Please forgive me for not joining forces.

161
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:31,639
Master, is Eldest Senior okay?

162
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:50,100
Xifan.

163
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,560
Master.

164
00:13:57,560 --> 00:14:01,580
I saw you peeking just now.

165
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:06,139
What's the matter? Are you feeling reluctant?

166
00:14:06,139 --> 00:14:10,680
Master, I know my own limits.

167
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:14,920
I shouldn't be going to the Pneuma Combat Convention.

168
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:17,579
I'm not the one controlling your legs.

169
00:14:17,579 --> 00:14:19,959
I'm not stopping you anyway.

170
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:26,160
An ambitious person needs a place to showcase his talent.

171
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:30,000
You've stayed at Wind Taker Institute for so many years.

172
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,240
It's time for you to go back to the path that you belong to.

173
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:38,879
I can't win against you.

174
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:41,379
I can't even win against Lu Ping.

175
00:14:41,379 --> 00:14:46,200
I didn't atone for my sins, so I can't hold a blade anymore.

176
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:49,600
Even if I go to the convention, I can't be of help.

177
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:53,320
Compared to you, Lu Ping is nothing.

178
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:56,080
Without Wind Taker Institute, Lu Ping wouldn't be like what he is now.

179
00:14:56,080 --> 00:15:00,420
But without you, the Wind Takers wouldn't be as the current Wind Takers.

180
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:07,220
Xing Luo are dead now.
(TN: Xing Luo were for both Situ Xing and Situ Luo)

181
00:15:09,379 --> 00:15:12,479
The weight is off your shoulders.

182
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,459
Stop it, Master!

183
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:18,399
My leg is injured, so whatever you say is pointless.

184
00:15:18,399 --> 00:15:20,819
It's too early to tell.

185
00:15:20,819 --> 00:15:23,039
Drink with me first.

186
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:30,099
I can tell from one glance, that this Zhao Xifan is different from you bumpkins.

187
00:15:30,099 --> 00:15:32,900
He has high self-esteem.

188
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:34,498
This thing you made.

189
00:15:34,498 --> 00:15:37,178
Could it really make him follow us to Kaifeng?

190
00:15:37,178 --> 00:15:41,920
Brother, all these years, after Eldest Senior joined the Wind Takers, he never returned home or went out.

191
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:43,819
I'm just afraid there's more to this than what's in front of us.

192
00:15:43,819 --> 00:15:46,679
Didn't Master give you any advice?

193
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,980
I think Master went drinking again.

194
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:52,939
He didn't leave any message.

195
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:57,940
After I finish this, send this to him on my behalf.

196
00:15:57,940 --> 00:16:00,199
I provoked Eldest Senior many times.

197
00:16:00,199 --> 00:16:03,340
It's better if you guys advise him.

198
00:16:04,859 --> 00:16:06,799
All of you are here?

199
00:16:06,799 --> 00:16:08,559
Lu Ping.

200
00:16:08,559 --> 00:16:11,219
When Master Guo bought the wine, he left this.

201
00:16:11,219 --> 00:16:15,039
He said he's buying time for you and asked me to pass this to you.

202
00:16:15,039 --> 00:16:17,840
He also said,

203
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,739
"the person who tied the bell..."

204
00:16:19,739 --> 00:16:22,338
- Should untie it.
- "Should untie it" yeah.

205
00:16:22,338 --> 00:16:24,400
Why are you holding the boards?

206
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:28,658
Isn't this our Ruyu House's chair?

207
00:16:28,658 --> 00:16:30,779
Why did it become like this?

208
00:16:34,499 --> 00:16:36,919
It's pretty comfortable.

209
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:48,320
Master, I should go now.

210
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,819
Don't! Not yet!

211
00:16:49,819 --> 00:16:51,920
Don't leave me.

212
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,980
You completely ignored my feelings.

213
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:59,460
The Wind Takers offended the Wei family this time.

214
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:02,679
If we don't get a placing in the convention,

215
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:09,260
the centuries-old organization will be ruined.

216
00:17:09,260 --> 00:17:12,759
Xifan, why don't you reconsider it? Can you?

217
00:17:12,759 --> 00:17:15,179
Master, I gave back the badge already.

218
00:17:15,179 --> 00:17:17,439
You should give it to a more suitable person.

219
00:17:17,439 --> 00:17:19,540
Eldest Senior.

220
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:22,678
I have something to return to you. Here!

221
00:17:25,659 --> 00:17:27,459
I already gave it back to Master.

222
00:17:27,459 --> 00:17:30,919
The Eldest Senior should be the Wind Takers' role model; it's better to give it to the God of Bandits.

223
00:17:30,919 --> 00:17:34,089
Nope, it's worthless! Even if it's a gift, I won't take it.

224
00:17:34,089 --> 00:17:35,500
You...

225
00:17:36,419 --> 00:17:38,839
Eldest Senior, it suits you more.

226
00:17:38,839 --> 00:17:40,450
Without you,

227
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:43,340
I won't be where I am now.

228
00:17:44,139 --> 00:17:47,380
I have my past and you also have your past.

229
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:51,379
Rather than running away, why don't we face it together?

230
00:17:51,379 --> 00:17:53,559
Yes, yes, yes.

231
00:17:56,720 --> 00:18:00,559
You said, your personal matters are none of my business, you can take it back now, right?

232
00:18:00,559 --> 00:18:03,200
I never take my words back.

233
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:05,780
Let's just say I want to get to know you again.

234
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:08,779
Wait for me! I have something for you.

235
00:18:28,759 --> 00:18:30,919
Your craftsmanship is pretty good.

236
00:18:30,919 --> 00:18:33,219
Come over here, give it a try!

237
00:18:33,219 --> 00:18:35,210
Come on!

238
00:18:37,659 --> 00:18:38,870
Come!

239
00:18:43,819 --> 00:18:45,119
Hold them!

240
00:18:47,619 --> 00:18:50,919
There's hope now to surpass the Big Dippers!

241
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:53,200
Move forward!

242
00:18:55,139 --> 00:18:58,178
Lu Ping, push him! Did you not eat?

243
00:19:14,759 --> 00:19:18,920
Chan State reported that you're already dead.

244
00:19:22,239 --> 00:19:26,559
I have important news to inform our Chief immediately.

245
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:37,490
I was heavily injured by the Wind Takers.

246
00:19:37,490 --> 00:19:39,920
I only dared to show myself after hiding for several days.

247
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,800
What a useless junk!

248
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:43,219
You embarrassed us.

249
00:19:43,219 --> 00:19:46,020
Why don't I pluck your teeth and make a necklace?

250
00:19:46,020 --> 00:19:48,400
The person concerns our Chief's grand plan.

251
00:19:51,519 --> 00:19:54,250
I rushed back to report this.

252
00:19:54,250 --> 00:19:59,510
I'm very sure that the person is the Awakener, who was kidnapped from the tower three years ago,

253
00:19:59,510 --> 00:20:01,319
Lu Ping.

254
00:20:06,319 --> 00:20:09,400
- Did you see him clearly?
- Yes.

255
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:15,439
I also heard that he's heading towards Kaifeng for the Pneuma Combat Convention.

256
00:20:17,179 --> 00:20:22,940
I'm willing to go to great lengths to capture him, so I can redeem myself.

257
00:20:22,940 --> 00:20:25,000
It's fine.

258
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:29,179
Since he already showed himself, he won't be able to escape again.

259
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:32,920
Nobody can walk away from Mountain and Sea Gang.

260
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:36,210
Dying here is his destiny.

261
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:43,699
As for you, you should know the rules of Mountain and Sea Gang.

262
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,800
Take her away!

263
00:20:55,119 --> 00:20:58,170
How are the arrangement at Kaifeng?

264
00:20:58,170 --> 00:21:00,659
Leader Feng has made the necessary preparations.

265
00:21:00,659 --> 00:21:03,599
Your plan may begin at any time.

266
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:07,999
Pass my order! Don't act rashly and alert the enemy.

267
00:21:07,999 --> 00:21:09,390
Yes.

268
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:21,520
[Kaifeng City]

269
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:25,919
The triennial Pneuma Combat Convention is around the corner.

270
00:21:25,919 --> 00:21:28,619
How are the preparations, Master Wen?

271
00:21:28,619 --> 00:21:35,180
Your Majesty, I already negotiated with General Qin and sent invitations to all martial arts academies

272
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:38,539
to recruit talented people from across the kingdom, so we can contribute to the kingdom.

273
00:21:38,539 --> 00:21:39,680
[Xia Bojian - Minister of Defense of the Shuo Kingdom]

274
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:45,279
Your Majesty, in my opinion, Master Wen's actions were inappropriate.

275
00:21:45,279 --> 00:21:46,619
[Chai Rong - Emperor of the Shuo Kingdom]

276
00:21:46,619 --> 00:21:49,890
Minister Xia, why do you say so?

277
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:54,959
The selection of generals concern the strength, the rise, and the fall of the kingdom.

278
00:21:54,959 --> 00:21:59,459
For generals of Shuo Kingdom, we should select them from prominent families by right.

279
00:21:59,459 --> 00:22:01,619
Your Majesty, a hero's origin isn't important.

280
00:22:01,619 --> 00:22:05,020
There are many extraordinary people in the martial arts world.

281
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:08,860
If we miss out on them, it will be Shuo Kingdom's loss.

282
00:22:08,860 --> 00:22:14,719
In terms of talent, many disciples of Shining Sky Academy have been enlisted over the years.

283
00:22:14,719 --> 00:22:17,359
All of them are excellent in martial arts.

284
00:22:17,359 --> 00:22:21,860
In terms of loyalty, imperial relatives come after prominent families.

285
00:22:21,860 --> 00:22:23,439
Their loyalty was indisputable.

286
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:27,719
How could the martial artists fare against them?

287
00:22:27,719 --> 00:22:31,940
I think that, General Qin has many acquaintances in the martial arts world,

288
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:36,340
especially the people with an unclear background and a suspicious motive.

289
00:22:36,340 --> 00:22:39,179
It's a disgrace to Shuo Kingdom.

290
00:22:39,179 --> 00:22:41,479
Minister Xia is also the headmaster of Shining Sky Academy.

291
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:44,519
Naturally, your disciples' capability can't be underestimated.

292
00:22:44,519 --> 00:22:47,680
But in my opinion, gathering talented people from all walks of life

293
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:50,260
is the only root of serving the imperial family.

294
00:22:50,260 --> 00:22:53,060
If you're afraid that commoners will overshadow the imperial family,

295
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:55,900
doesn't this go against the imperial graciousness?

296
00:22:57,699 --> 00:22:59,580
General, you just returned.

297
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:01,340
You should, at least, take off your armor first .

298
00:23:01,340 --> 00:23:04,920
While I'm absent, Minister Xia won't waste this opportunity for sure.

299
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:07,519
I can't let Master Wen suffer alone.

300
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:12,980
My two officials, you've been planning for this martial arts event.

301
00:23:12,980 --> 00:23:15,140
You want the best for the kingdom.

302
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:17,239
Please don't be impatient!

303
00:23:17,239 --> 00:23:20,260
- Your Majesty.
- Agile Dragon Army's General,

304
00:23:20,260 --> 00:23:23,780
Qin Qi requests to be presented.

305
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:25,180
Summon him!

306
00:23:33,780 --> 00:23:36,080
Greetings, Your Majesty.

307
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:38,658
General Qin, you must've had a tiring journey.

308
00:23:38,658 --> 00:23:41,659
Serving the kingdom is my pleasure.

309
00:23:41,659 --> 00:23:47,018
Your Majesty, I heard the martial arts academies are planning to send their disciples to take part in this convention.

310
00:23:47,018 --> 00:23:50,138
Shuo Kingdom's martial artists have never been gathered together.

311
00:23:50,138 --> 00:23:52,760
It's the blessing of Shuo Kingdom.

312
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:55,920
I'm afraid Minister Xia doesn't believe so.

313
00:23:56,680 --> 00:24:02,098
Does Minister Xia still believe that generals should only be from prominent families?

314
00:24:02,098 --> 00:24:03,499
Exactly so!

315
00:24:03,499 --> 00:24:07,299
Your Qin family is prominent and valiant.

316
00:24:07,299 --> 00:24:10,679
They have also cultivated a talented person like General Qin.

317
00:24:10,679 --> 00:24:12,299
This proves my point.

318
00:24:12,299 --> 00:24:16,178
Lieutenant general of Left Guard Corps, Li Che, graduated from Chan State Academy.

319
00:24:16,178 --> 00:24:18,439
Since he took office to suppress the northwestern bandits,

320
00:24:18,439 --> 00:24:21,079
he performed a total of 35 meritorious services.

321
00:24:21,079 --> 00:24:25,018
Lieutenant general of Imperial Martial Artists, Fang Qiong graduated from Xu State Academy.

322
00:24:25,018 --> 00:24:26,340
This person was a genius.

323
00:24:26,340 --> 00:24:29,299
He invented Horse Splitting Formation and fought countless enemies.

324
00:24:29,299 --> 00:24:31,558
Since Master Wen conducts the army selection,

325
00:24:31,558 --> 00:24:35,620
many generals selected from the commoners are talented.

326
00:24:35,620 --> 00:24:41,020
But some people from prominent families are incompetent and corrupted.

327
00:24:41,020 --> 00:24:45,559
I believe Minister Xia is clearly aware of this.

328
00:24:45,559 --> 00:24:49,799
More importantly, the citizens are in turmoil over the years. Really unstable!

329
00:24:49,799 --> 00:24:51,979
The citizens are fighting against oppression.

330
00:24:51,979 --> 00:24:56,759
If we can unite the citizens and put them to good use through the Pneuma Combat Convention,

331
00:24:56,759 --> 00:25:00,358
we won't have to worry about Shuo Kingdom's prosperity and stability.

332
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,938
Your Majesty, please forgive my bluntness.

333
00:25:04,938 --> 00:25:08,079
During this convention, you're not only selecting generals,

334
00:25:08,079 --> 00:25:11,339
you're also raising the ambitious and fighting spirit of the kingdom.

335
00:25:11,339 --> 00:25:13,160
Nicely spoken!

336
00:25:15,060 --> 00:25:20,200
This Pneuma Combat Convention is to enlighten the pneumatic power of Shuo Kingdom.

337
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:25,390
General Qin, I'm looking forward to the kind of talented heroes

338
00:25:25,390 --> 00:25:30,800
you and Master Wen will select for our Great Shuo

339
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:33,640
during this Pneuma Combat Convention.

340
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:38,620
We won't disappoint, Your Majesty.

341
00:25:44,020 --> 00:25:45,960
General Qin.

342
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:55,100
General Qin, you sounded sure of yourself in the court today.

343
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:59,899
But I still hope that the martial artists you recommend

344
00:25:59,899 --> 00:26:03,259
can be like you, too, to not disappoint His Majesty.

345
00:26:03,259 --> 00:26:07,599
Please look forward to it then, Minister Xia.

346
00:26:21,819 --> 00:26:24,679
Wenrui, I'll send Master Wen home.

347
00:26:24,679 --> 00:26:26,518
Find a doctor for a check-up.

348
00:26:26,518 --> 00:26:27,558
Yes.

349
00:26:27,559 --> 00:26:31,658
I'm fine, General! It's just a relapse of my old injury.

350
00:26:31,658 --> 00:26:36,480
In the court just now, thank you for fighting for me.

351
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:39,938
But at this rate, the hatred between Minister Xia and you grows deeper.

352
00:26:39,938 --> 00:26:41,760
Since there's already a grudge,

353
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:45,079
just leave it be if I can't resolve it.

354
00:26:45,999 --> 00:26:50,040
General, you should plan for your own future.

355
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:52,659
I'm just an ordinary guy from the martial arts world.

356
00:26:52,659 --> 00:26:54,419
Don't worry about me!

357
00:26:54,419 --> 00:26:56,119
Master Wen,

358
00:26:56,119 --> 00:27:00,398
all these years, if you didn't discuss martial arts with me and organize military affairs,

359
00:27:00,398 --> 00:27:03,158
you won't become a thorn in Xia Bojian's flesh.

360
00:27:03,158 --> 00:27:08,638
Not to mention, if I protect you, I'm also protecting the talented people of the future who will work for Shuo Kingdom.

361
00:27:08,638 --> 00:27:14,760
Master Wen, do you still remember what I said when we were organizing the Pneuma Combat Convention back then?

362
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:16,240
I still remember.

363
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:18,938
"The Qin family conquered the world with the previous emperor."

364
00:27:18,938 --> 00:27:21,960
"Knowing that soldiers are the roots of a kingdom."

365
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:24,919
"If I can bring talented martial artists to Shuo Kingdom,"

366
00:27:24,919 --> 00:27:29,839
"even if I have to go against the whole world, I, Qin Qi, am not afraid."

367
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:34,979
I'm amazed by your lofty spirit.

368
00:27:34,979 --> 00:27:39,678
I'll definitely handle the Pneuma Combat Convention well, so I'll live up to your expectations.

369
00:27:39,678 --> 00:27:45,898
Come with me now! After you rest well, the Pneuma Combat Convention still needs you as a host.

370
00:27:45,898 --> 00:27:49,299
Also, Sang'er...

371
00:27:49,299 --> 00:27:52,139
Sang'er has been wanting to meet you for a long time.

372
00:27:52,139 --> 00:27:56,840
Did Miss create some sort of trouble again and needed you to deal with it?

373
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:05,359
I instructed you guys not hold back.

374
00:28:05,359 --> 00:28:09,378
All of you are pulling your punches, what's the point of fighting?

375
00:28:09,378 --> 00:28:11,380
Dismiss!

376
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:12,959
- Yes.
- Yes.

377
00:28:12,959 --> 00:28:16,458
You fought three people previously; now, you can fight five people.

378
00:28:16,458 --> 00:28:18,500
It seems you've made progress.

379
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:22,219
I heard that when you were at my age, you can fight ten people.

380
00:28:22,219 --> 00:28:24,720
Why don't you train with me?

381
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:28,198
When I train the Sun Streamer Swordplay with Ziyan, she always holds back.

382
00:28:28,198 --> 00:28:29,458
It's suffocating.

383
00:28:29,458 --> 00:28:31,200
Ziyan!

384
00:28:34,659 --> 00:28:37,178
You instructed me before that I can't train with Miss.

385
00:28:37,178 --> 00:28:40,458
I have crossed the line, please forgive me.

386
00:28:46,659 --> 00:28:48,920
It was I who ordered Ziyan.

387
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:55,819
I know the Sun Streamer Swordplay can't be divulged but I need someone to counter my moves, don't I?

388
00:28:55,819 --> 00:28:58,438
You love roaming the world, I allowed you.

389
00:28:58,438 --> 00:29:01,500
However, the Sun Streamer Swordplay is the Qin family's secret sword technique.

390
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:04,399
Once it's divulged, it disturbs our clan's foundation.

391
00:29:04,399 --> 00:29:06,939
Did you totally ignore what I said?

392
00:29:09,179 --> 00:29:12,659
You two, accept your punishments based on the family rules.

393
00:29:14,659 --> 00:29:16,400
Go now!

394
00:29:20,340 --> 00:29:24,019
Don't get angry, General! Let me be the mediator.

395
00:29:24,019 --> 00:29:28,438
The Pneuma Combat Convention is upon us, why don't we make a deal here?

396
00:29:28,438 --> 00:29:33,399
If Miss Qin wins the convention, then Miss Ling's and her punishments will be revoked.

397
00:29:33,399 --> 00:29:37,819
If Miss Qin didn't manage to pass, she'll accept your punishment without any objection.

398
00:29:37,819 --> 00:29:39,559
What do you think?

399
00:29:39,559 --> 00:29:40,838
- Master Wen...
- All right!

400
00:29:40,839 --> 00:29:44,079
It's just a convention, I'll win and show it to you.

401
00:29:44,079 --> 00:29:46,400
What do you think, General?

402
00:29:48,419 --> 00:29:49,960
Fine!

403
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:53,580
She won't listen to anyone but Master Wen.

404
00:29:53,580 --> 00:29:57,880
However, let me tell you! Don't expect Master Wen to cheat for you.

405
00:29:57,880 --> 00:30:00,358
If you want to win, you must rely on your own strength.

406
00:30:00,359 --> 00:30:04,518
If I ask Uncle Wen to guide me in martial arts, it's not cheating, right?

407
00:30:04,518 --> 00:30:06,359
Uncle Wen, please!

408
00:30:14,119 --> 00:30:17,280
Uncle Wen, you're the most knowledgeable.

409
00:30:17,280 --> 00:30:21,720
Have you heard of a chain that can bind one's Pneuma of Strength?

410
00:30:22,859 --> 00:30:26,599
Why did you suddenly ask this, Miss?

411
00:30:26,599 --> 00:30:27,898
You do know?

412
00:30:27,898 --> 00:30:30,440
Then do you know how to unbind it?

413
00:30:30,980 --> 00:30:35,099
Indeed, there's something called the Bloodline Technique to unlock the Pneuma Confinement

414
00:30:35,099 --> 00:30:37,078
but it's rare and complicated.

415
00:30:37,078 --> 00:30:42,820
As to whether it can be unbound, it depends on the person.

416
00:30:42,820 --> 00:30:46,200
Have you seen this kind of martial arts?

417
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:06,359
Why am I concerned about that rogue?

418
00:31:07,260 --> 00:31:11,039
I must concentrate to train my swordsmanship.

419
00:31:11,039 --> 00:31:14,759
I must perform well during the Pneuma Combat Convention.

420
00:31:16,659 --> 00:31:18,780
I heard it from a young bandit.

421
00:31:18,780 --> 00:31:22,618
Uncle Wen, I'll get a cup of tea for you and we'll continue with the training later.

422
00:31:41,340 --> 00:31:43,378
"Preparations are made in Kaifeng."

423
00:31:43,378 --> 00:31:47,318
"Our Chief orders you to stop chasing after Lu Ping and stay in Chan State for further instructions."

424
00:31:47,318 --> 00:31:50,659
"Failing again won't be forgivable."

425
00:31:50,659 --> 00:31:54,279
How gracious His Lord is! It's not our time yet.

426
00:31:54,279 --> 00:31:56,539
The Wei family is safe for now.

427
00:31:56,539 --> 00:31:57,798
What about our future?

428
00:31:57,798 --> 00:32:00,299
Let's take one step at a time.

429
00:32:00,299 --> 00:32:04,119
Our lives are in the hands of others.

430
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:06,680
Father.

431
00:32:07,459 --> 00:32:09,799
Father, I've decided.

432
00:32:09,799 --> 00:32:13,200
Father, why are you sweating?

433
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:16,878
The weather is so hot, it's too stuffy! What do you need?

434
00:32:16,878 --> 00:32:18,439
I want to go to Kaifeng for the convention.

435
00:32:18,439 --> 00:32:20,959
If I'm famous, I'll be worthy of Sangsang.

436
00:32:20,959 --> 00:32:22,480
Young Master.

437
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,019
Go if you must!

438
00:32:24,019 --> 00:32:28,438
Wei Ming, let Wei Ying bring the bodyguards with the best martial arts to protect Young Master.

439
00:32:28,438 --> 00:32:30,720
Thank you, Father! I'll write a letter now.

440
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,799
I want to tell Sangsang.

441
00:32:38,559 --> 00:32:41,760
Master, Lu Ping is at Kaifeng, too.

442
00:32:41,760 --> 00:32:44,000
It's better to avoid him right now.

443
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:46,459
The Mountain and Sea Gang's punishment is hanging over our heads.

444
00:32:46,459 --> 00:32:48,838
We are walking on thin ice already.

445
00:32:48,838 --> 00:32:51,378
Let Tianqi do whatever he wants.

446
00:32:51,378 --> 00:32:53,739
The Mountain and Sea Gang treats Lu Ping indifferently.

447
00:32:53,739 --> 00:32:56,698
Tell Wei Ying to protect Tianqi this time!

448
00:32:56,698 --> 00:33:00,019
Don't let him get involved with Lu Ping.

449
00:33:00,019 --> 00:33:01,540
Yes.

450
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:22,299
I can't! I can't walk anymore.

451
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:32,358
Guo Youdao, didn't you get a lot of silver taels from Wei Zhong?

452
00:33:32,358 --> 00:33:34,859
Can't you hire a carriage?

453
00:33:34,859 --> 00:33:36,819
How dare you!

454
00:33:36,819 --> 00:33:39,280
The martial arts tower was so expensive.

455
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:41,620
I gave them to Chan State Academy.

456
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:44,720
Be thankful that we don't have to beg for food!

457
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:47,159
Martial arts practitioners shouldn't crave for comfort.

458
00:33:47,159 --> 00:33:49,558
It's easy for you to talk! You've been sitting all along.

459
00:33:49,558 --> 00:33:52,060
My disciple was pushing you.

460
00:33:52,060 --> 00:33:55,599
Mo Lin, do you want to sleep here

461
00:33:55,599 --> 00:33:59,800
or do you want to sleep on a bed in Kaifeng City with a full stomach?

462
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:09,488
Isn't this Miss Qin's golden badge?

463
00:34:09,488 --> 00:34:14,198
Lu Ping, let's go to Kaifeng quickly so we can stay in the most luxurious guest room.

464
00:34:14,198 --> 00:34:15,509
- Yes.
- No way!

465
00:34:15,509 --> 00:34:18,658
Using someone's name to deceive people, how is it different from stealing?

466
00:34:18,658 --> 00:34:20,790
Xifan, catch on when one is poor.

467
00:34:20,790 --> 00:34:23,380
Look at him! He can't give up on his principles.

468
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:27,299
Wind Takers must be honorable! Master, this is what you taught us.

469
00:34:27,299 --> 00:34:29,558
- What should we eat?
- We must eat chicken.

470
00:34:29,558 --> 00:34:31,378
- Yes.
- Yes.

471
00:34:31,378 --> 00:34:33,579
Let me think about it.

472
00:34:33,579 --> 00:34:36,488
One whole chicken isn't enough because I, alone, can eat half a chicken.

473
00:34:36,488 --> 00:34:38,440
Let's order two, then.

474
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:51,039
[Shining Sky Academy]

475
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:57,518
Miss, it has been a while since you returned to Shining Sky Academy but you refuse to enter.

476
00:34:57,518 --> 00:35:00,379
Don't you want to visit your peers?

477
00:35:00,379 --> 00:35:03,529
Ziyan, I was here for three years

478
00:35:03,529 --> 00:35:05,820
but I attended classes for less than three months.

479
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:08,000
Do you know why?

480
00:35:10,429 --> 00:35:13,298
Shining Sky Academy only accepts disciples from prominent families.

481
00:35:13,298 --> 00:35:16,809
It's not about martial arts but one's family background.

482
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:21,960
This type of place isn't as interesting as the Wind Taker Institute.

483
00:35:23,389 --> 00:35:25,289
Junior Qin.

484
00:35:26,739 --> 00:35:28,559
Senior Luo Ting.

485
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:30,258
Congratulations, Junior.

486
00:35:30,258 --> 00:35:33,738
For the Pneuma Combat Convention, you and I are selected.
[Luo Ting - Shining Sky Academy Disciple]

487
00:35:33,738 --> 00:35:36,979
I wonder if you're interested in forming a team.

488
00:35:36,979 --> 00:35:38,839
Thank you for the kind offer.

489
00:35:38,839 --> 00:35:41,929
Ziyan and I will find two more disciples.

490
00:35:41,929 --> 00:35:44,428
You are highly respected at Shining Sky Academy,

491
00:35:44,428 --> 00:35:47,159
I believe you have better candidates than me.

492
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:56,139
A slave who is protected by you has become a disciple of Shining Sky Academy in exchange.

493
00:35:56,139 --> 00:35:58,359
She's not worth it.

494
00:35:58,359 --> 00:36:02,159
Plus, I heard that you had just returned from experiencing the martial arts world.

495
00:36:02,159 --> 00:36:04,488
You're from a prominent family after all.

496
00:36:04,488 --> 00:36:08,099
Roaming among commoners in the martial arts world goes against the decorum.

497
00:36:08,099 --> 00:36:10,718
Why don't you mingle with us?

498
00:36:10,718 --> 00:36:13,519
That's only fitting for your identity.

499
00:36:16,540 --> 00:36:19,620
I don't care about one's identity.

500
00:36:19,620 --> 00:36:21,819
I only look at one's martial arts.

501
00:36:21,819 --> 00:36:24,518
In addition, the world's martial artists come from all walks of life.

502
00:36:24,518 --> 00:36:26,979
There's no shortage of talented people.

503
00:36:26,979 --> 00:36:31,758
Since you're going to the Pneuma Combat Convention, I believe you'll witness it very soon.

504
00:36:33,529 --> 00:36:36,000
Ziyan, let's go!

505
00:36:41,599 --> 00:36:46,878
Senior Luo, you're from a prominent family and Headmaster Xia's favorite disciple.

506
00:36:46,878 --> 00:36:49,618
[Qiao Ying - Shining Sky Academy Disciple]
[Shi Zhongtian - Shining Sky Academy Disciple] 
If the Qin family didn't organize the Pneuma Combat Convention,

507
00:36:49,618 --> 00:36:51,918
you would have already joined the military as an official.

508
00:36:51,918 --> 00:36:54,979
You won't have to fight with those world's martial artists.

509
00:36:54,979 --> 00:36:59,499
You're broad-minded so you chose not to argue with her but she has gotten worse, instead.

510
00:36:59,499 --> 00:37:02,239
She said you're worse than her maid.

511
00:37:03,079 --> 00:37:07,289
[Hongfu Inn]

512
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:31,738
If I knew the Qin family is so powerful in Kaifeng,

513
00:37:31,738 --> 00:37:35,399
I would've asked for one that doubles the price from Qin Sang back then.

514
00:37:35,399 --> 00:37:38,338
At this point in time, do you still want to kill Lu Ping?

515
00:37:38,338 --> 00:37:42,159
Not really! How can I touch our boss?

516
00:37:42,159 --> 00:37:44,618
Right, Su Tang! Do you like this room?

517
00:37:44,618 --> 00:37:48,508
It's the most expensive! I have a good taste after all.

518
00:37:49,499 --> 00:37:54,000
All right! Let's keep this room for my brother.

519
00:37:55,179 --> 00:37:56,980
Where is my brother?

520
00:38:06,689 --> 00:38:09,309
Here! If you don't change the dressing,

521
00:38:09,309 --> 00:38:12,079
don't dream of walking again.

522
00:38:12,659 --> 00:38:14,798
Did you cheat again using Qin family's golden badge?

523
00:38:14,798 --> 00:38:17,539
- Don't need it?
- No need!

524
00:38:17,539 --> 00:38:19,129
All right.

525
00:38:19,129 --> 00:38:22,909
Lu Ping, don't you want to fight against Mountain and Sea Gang?

526
00:38:22,909 --> 00:38:25,338
Can you change your bad habits and be a good person?

527
00:38:25,338 --> 00:38:27,299
Eldest Senior,

528
00:38:27,299 --> 00:38:30,899
good people will not only die but they will die even faster.

529
00:38:30,899 --> 00:38:32,769
This is the principle.

530
00:38:34,139 --> 00:38:38,240
When you can walk on your own, let's talk about your principles, then.

531
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:39,819
- Lu Ping!
- Lu Ping!

532
00:38:40,829 --> 00:38:43,118
- Master.
- Lu Ping, go and take a look inside quickly.

533
00:38:43,118 --> 00:38:45,299
The interior is so luxurious.

534
00:38:45,299 --> 00:38:47,119
Hurry up!

535
00:38:53,219 --> 00:38:56,658
Looking at you, it seems you're determined to sleep outside.

536
00:38:56,658 --> 00:39:00,359
I have never stayed in such a nice guest room.

537
00:39:00,359 --> 00:39:02,339
I won't accompany you then.

538
00:39:02,339 --> 00:39:04,089
Master!

539
00:39:07,679 --> 00:39:09,419
Help me up!

540
00:39:17,919 --> 00:39:20,198
Have you changed your mind for one?

541
00:39:20,198 --> 00:39:22,739
If I don't rest well and get back on my feet,

542
00:39:22,739 --> 00:39:25,639
that guy, Lu Ping, is going to be on the ninth level of cloud.
(TN: Clouds have 9 levels with the 9th is the highest - one is most elated)

543
00:39:33,639 --> 00:39:37,739
Very good! Your provocation is working.

544
00:39:40,529 --> 00:39:42,599
Lu Ping, come here!

545
00:39:46,439 --> 00:39:48,039
What's the matter?

546
00:39:48,909 --> 00:39:51,360
For you to succeed,

547
00:39:51,360 --> 00:39:55,718
I have prepared specifically an affordable gift for you.

548
00:39:55,718 --> 00:39:57,539
You have a gift for me?

549
00:40:04,799 --> 00:40:08,000
Master, use it when you pray for our founding master.

550
00:40:08,000 --> 00:40:09,939
I don't need it.

551
00:40:10,969 --> 00:40:14,039
Since the day in the tower, I broke another chain of the Pneuma Confinement Lock.

552
00:40:14,039 --> 00:40:16,808
The usage of my Pneuma of Strength isn't limited to burning one joss stick anymore.

553
00:40:16,808 --> 00:40:19,900
I think I can handle the convention.

554
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:25,919
I already taught you most of the things I know.

555
00:40:25,919 --> 00:40:31,079
Only this Kaifeng City can teach you the remaining things.

556
00:40:32,219 --> 00:40:33,959
Do you guys smell it?

557
00:40:33,959 --> 00:40:36,300
The Mountain and Sea Gang?

558
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:39,539
Mountain and Sea Gang, Mountain and Sea Gang! Other than escaping, can you think of something else?

559
00:40:39,539 --> 00:40:43,818
It's congee! The most famous congee in Kaifeng City.

560
00:40:47,869 --> 00:40:50,518
Young Master, the Pneuma Combat Convention is near.

561
00:40:50,518 --> 00:40:53,138
Master reminded me to be wary of your work-sleep balance.

562
00:40:53,138 --> 00:40:56,500
Where do you want to have your meal today?

563
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:59,979
Not meeting Sangsang, my heart is filled with sadness.

564
00:40:59,979 --> 00:41:02,559
Let's have something light.

565
00:41:04,139 --> 00:41:06,039
[Yuyangji Congee Store]

566
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:15,099
Honorable guests of the Qin family, although our shop is small,

567
00:41:15,099 --> 00:41:18,818
this crab congee is the one and only in Kaifeng City.

568
00:41:18,818 --> 00:41:20,600
Please enjoy!

569
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:22,908
River crab, Japonica rice, and parsley.

570
00:41:22,908 --> 00:41:25,399
Nothing more, nothing less!

571
00:41:25,399 --> 00:41:29,359
Martial arts practitioners shouldn't crave for good food.

572
