Eldest Senior, martial arts practitioners aren't monks.

573
00:41:33,318 --> 00:41:34,780
Here!

574
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:46,828
Zhao Xifan, I'm cultivating Pneuma of Pivot.

575
00:41:46,828 --> 00:41:50,679
Perception is my focus, so not only must I eat, I must eat good food.

576
00:41:50,679 --> 00:41:54,159
Nobody wants to live an ascetic life like you.

