587
00:42:42,218 --> 00:42:46,129
Don't you feel bad for all my sweat and tears to come here?

588
00:42:46,129 --> 00:42:49,020
Enemies often cross each other's path, don't you think so?

589
00:42:49,020 --> 00:42:52,009
Shop keeper, do you know who my father is?

590
00:42:52,009 --> 00:42:54,298
Have you heard of Chan State's Wei family?

591
00:42:54,298 --> 00:42:56,919
I'm the young master of the Wei family.

