597
00:43:20,689 --> 00:43:24,359
No matter what, I want the private seats.

598
00:43:24,359 --> 00:43:27,259
Wei Hu, throw them out!

599
00:43:27,259 --> 00:43:31,759
Young Master, Master instructed us that we must keep a low profile in Kaifeng.

600
00:43:31,759 --> 00:43:34,000
If you don't do it, I'll do it myself.

601
00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:40,079
- My Guest.
- Move aside!

602
00:43:40,079 --> 00:43:42,940
- My Guest, don't smash anything!
- Go!

